headline: Air France KLM Reshapes US Europe Network And Balance Sheet Profile
summary: Air France-KLM is stepping up its US–Europe offering, adding capacity at major US hubs while tightening its partnerships with Delta Air Lines and Virgin Atlantic. The group is refreshing its fleet with more fuel efficient aircraft and has recently reduced debt that was built up during the pandemic period. Together, these moves point to a shift in how the airline is positioning its long term business across profitability, resilience and environmental impact. For investors watching ENXTPA:AF,...
